Linear Regression: Predicts Continuous data.

Categorical / Discrete
Continuous - Uses Linear Regression to predict future

y axis - What you want to predict
x axis - Data used to make prediction (feature or 'predictor')

Simple Linear Regression - Uses ONE feature to predict the future.
Multiple Linear Regression - Uses more than one predictor to determine the future.

Beta Values - 

y = mx + b

y = $ amount
m = slope
x = sq. footage
b = y - intercept

OLS - Ordinary Least Squares - 

http://setosa.io/ev/ordinary-least-squares-regression/
